textList: Courses appearing in the Major GPA Course Summary are for the calculation
of the major GPA.  Major courses with an earned grade of 'F' are
included in the major GPA calculation but will
ONLY appear in the Work Not Applicable to any Program portion of the
audit.  Courses that appear within course rules which contain the text
'(Excluded from Major GPA)' are not included in the major GPA but are,
nevertheless, part of the coursework that comprise the major.
